@host = http://localhost:9090

### 매출 등록 - 정상 케이스
POST {{host}}/api/sales
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseId": 1,
  "studentId": 100,
  "paymentAmount": 50000,
  "paidAt": "2026-05-22T10:00:00"
}

### 매출 등록 - 결제 금액 0 (무료 강의)
POST {{host}}/api/sales
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseId": 1,
  "studentId": 101,
  "paymentAmount": 0,
  "paidAt": "2026-05-22T10:00:00"
}

### 매출 등록 - validation 실패 확인용 (paymentAmount 음수)
POST {{host}}/api/sales
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseId": 1,
  "studentId": 100,
  "paymentAmount": -1000,
  "paidAt": "2026-05-22T10:00:00"
}

### 매출 등록 - validation 실패 확인용 (필수 필드 누락)
POST {{host}}/api/sales
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseId": 1,
  "paymentAmount": 50000
}
